Nice — you want FAANG-level, industry-grade prompts you (or your team) can paste into an LLM (Claude / GPT) to drive every major Standor task: design, code, refactor, infra, tests, docs, PRs, interviews, triage, release notes, security, performance, and onboarding. Below I give a curated, organized set of high-quality prompt templates (ready to paste) plus short guidance for how to use each one and what to expect. Use these prompts as your “engineer’s prompt library” — they’re written to get precise, production-ready outputs.

